Public Container As Block                 '' Apunta al contenedor de esta entidad, util para UnDo y Redo
Public Group As Collection                  '' Grupos temporales de entidades. Esto apunta al grupo donde estoy o Null
Public Psel As New Boolean[]                '' Selected points
Public Polygon As New Float[]               '' This is a poligon built at element's contruction that defines a poligon used for detecting points inside me
Public PolyLine As New Float[]              '' This is a polyline built at element's contruction that defines a poligon used for detecting points inside me
'Public PoiPoints As New Float[]             '' Point of interest
Public PoiType As New Integer[]
Public glDrwList As Integer                 '' OpenGL drawing list
Public glDrwListSel As Integer              '' OpenGL drawing list for selected item
Public glDrwListRemark As Integer           '' OpenGL drawing list for remarked item
Public glDrwListPOI As Integer              '' OpenGL drawing list for POI (grips)
